item.title: PACEY'S INTERNATIONAL BREAK
item.description: This week on Big Kick Suzi tells us about who she had in her audience at the weekend, we discuss all the action from the Champions League and League cup, chat to Louise McIvor from the LGBT Foundation about the work the foundation does around women's football, look ahead to the last Lioness games of the year and read a very special match report from 9 year old Elodie...
